flowchart TD
    A([Customer Login]) --> B[Browse Catalogue<br/><i>Personalised pricing</i>]
    B --> C[Search / Filter Products]
    C --> D[Add Items to Cart]
    D --> E{Continue<br/>Shopping?}
    E -->|Yes| B
    E -->|No| F[View Cart<br/><i>Shows budget status</i>]
    F --> G[Checkout]
    G --> H{Individual<br/>Budget OK?}
    H -->|No| I[❌ Blocked<br/><i>Individual budget exceeded</i>]
    H -->|Yes| J{Company<br/>Budget OK?}
    J -->|No| K[❌ Blocked<br/><i>Company budget exceeded</i>]
    J -->|Yes| L[✅ PO Created]
    L --> M[Confirmation Email<br/><i>To customer + Evergreen</i>]
    L --> N[Budget Updated<br/><i>Individual + Company</i>]
    L --> O[Order in Admin Queue<br/><i>For fulfilment</i>]

